  <title>Antimicrobial activity against Xanthomonas albilineans and fermentation kinetics of a lactic acid bacterium isolated from the sugar cane crop</title>
  <URL>https://cn.bing.com/academic/profile?id=0fc0b55fabb2e9308bf76db452951d33&amp;encoded=0&amp;v=paper_preview&amp;mkt=zh-cn</URL>
